originalText.text: Dr. Sinensky is the best dentist I've had in years. I've found her to be skilled, personable and highly reputable. I feel very comfortable trusting her recommendations with regard to my dental care and I actually feel like she cares about me as a person, not just a "customer". Her new dental office is bright, modern, clean and very easily accessible. The team working at the front desk and in the rest of the office were super friendly, talented and efficient. Highly recommended!

originalText.text: Dr. Sinensky is amazing! Let me start off by saying, I have a history of being petrified when going to the dentist. Leading up to my dental implant procedure I was super anxious. Dr. Sinensky put my mind at ease throughout the process. I’m shocked how easy it actually was (for me). She is patient, super intelligent and just a really nice person. Going to dental house has changed my feelings about going to the dentist. They make you feel so calm. The entire staff is wonderful. They really do care about your experience. I will NEVER go to another place for my dental work. I actually look forward to going to the dentist now. The best!

originalText.text: If you had a bad experience with  dentists in the past, Dr. Sinebsky will change your mind about that.  First, the ladies at the front desk is so welcoming and helpful.  You feel at ease once you get there.  I went to Dental House to get a consultation about tooth extraction.  Dr. Sinensky kept my mind at ease and told me what to expect. I appreciate her honesty.  The procedure went well and quickly. I'm writing this review the day after my procedure and my mouth feels fine.  Just a little soreness. Of course, that's expected. If you need a new dentist or you're scared about getting a procedure done, please check them out. They will make you feel at ease.
